{"type": "article", "id": 29277, "title": "挂颈式蓝牙耳机", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-07T23:03:25Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 59, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160707161919vcnxiAXqzOGfSIL3.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>以北欧简约风格闻名的丹麦品牌 <a href=\"http://www.bang-olufsen.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bang &amp; Olufsen</a> 最近推出了首款挂颈式的蓝牙无线耳机 Beoplay H5，主打便携性以及百搭的造型。受到高档运动鞋带的启发，耳机线外包有编织线，织物材质不仅舒适而且便于清理，还能够防止灰尘和汗水产生电子干扰。耳机的外壳则采用了橡胶和聚合物制成，拥有防潮的功能，无论是在家中还是户外都很适用。耳机各内置了一块小磁铁，可以很轻松地挂在脖子上，不用担心会找不到，当它们因为磁性触碰在一起后，耳机还会自动断电，延长续航的时间。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/PLAY-Bang-Olufsen-Headphone-1643426/dp/B01G48RH20\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 249 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707162016t7QikfRgYaSJzqOc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.580685\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607071620170EyxtiPgaRMoFTkh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607071620175PavxCusb3kp9rRe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707162017CFPr9EgxWTZNGjyv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}